high_descs: Turn walk forward then turn left then right to face the corner of the bath tub.
Pick up the bar of soap from the side of the tub.
Step to the right and face the tub.
Place the bar of soap inside the tub.
Turn to the right and face the toilet.
Pick up the bar of soap from the back end of the toilet.
Turn to the left and go back to the tub.
Place the bar of soap in the tub.
anns.task_desc: Place two bars of soap in the tub.

high_descs: Walk forward, then turn left and walk across the room to the wall and turn right to face the tub.
Pick up the bar of soap off of the tub.
Turn right and walk forward, then turn left and walk up to the tub.
Put the bar of soap into the tub.
Turn right and walk forward, then turn left and walk up to the toilet.
Pick up the bar of soap off of the toilet tank.
Turn around and walk forward, then turn right and walk over to the tub.
Put the bar of soap into the tub.
anns.task_desc: Move two bars of soap into the tub.

high_descs: Turn left and go to the left side of the bath tub in the right corner.
Pick up the pink sponge on the edge of the tub.
Move to the middle of the bath tub.
Place the pink sponge in the left corner of the bath tub.
Move over right to the front of the toilet .
Pick up the pink sponge on the top of the toilet tank.
Turn left and go back to the left corner of the bath tub.
Place the pink sponge on the right of the first sponge in the bath tub.
anns.task_desc: Move two pink sponges into the bath tub.
